question.string: Which artist made the albums Blackout and Circus?

question.query: PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX mo: <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/> SELECT DISTINCT ?maker1 ?name1 WHERE { ?album1 dc:title 'Blackout' . ?album2 dc:title 'Circus' . ?album1 foaf:maker ?maker1 . ?album2 foaf:maker ?maker2 . ?maker1 foaf:name ?name1 . ?maker2 foaf:name ?name2 . FILTER (regex(?name1, ?name2)) }

question.string: With whom did Phil Collins work together?
question.query: PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX rel: <http://purl.org/vocab/relationship/> PREFIX mo: <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/> SELECT DISTINCT ?artist2 ?name WHERE { ?artist foaf:name 'Phil Collins' . ?artist rel:collaboratesWith ?collaboration . ?artist2 foaf:name ?name . ?artist2 rel:collaboratesWith ?collaboration . }

queryInterpretation.descriptiveSentence: Collaborate created by <b>un(e) person<\/b>, from the album Phil Collins
queryInterpretation.sparqlQuery:
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX mo: <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?person WHERE { ?collaborate_with (rdfs:label|dc:title|foaf:name) "Collaborate".
?collaborate_with rdf:type <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/Track>.
?person rdf:type <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent>. ?collaborate_with <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/maker> ?person. ?Phil_Collins rdf:type <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/Record>. ?Phil_Collins (rdfs:label|dc:title|foaf:name) "Phil Collins". ?Phil_Collins <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/track> ?collaborate_with. }
